{"title":"Vuex (未完待續)","date":"2020-07-12T05:26:01.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 12, 2020","L":"07/12/2020","MM-DD":"07-12"},"link":"2020/07/12/vuex","tags":["frameWork","vue"],"updated":"2020-07-12T14:02:51.877Z","content":"<html><head></head><body><h2 id=\"Vuex-是什麼？\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/07/12/vuex#Vuex-是什麼？\"></a>Vuex 是什麼？</h2>\n<p>每一個Vuex應用的核心就是<font color=\"red\">store（倉庫）</font>。“store”基本上就是一個容器，它包含著你的應用中大部分的狀態(state)。Vuex和單純的全局對像有以下兩點不同：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Vuex 的狀態存儲是<mark>響應式</mark>的。當Vue 組件從store 中讀取狀態的時候，若store 中的狀態發生變化，那麼相應的組件也會相應地得到高效更新。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>你<font color=\"red\">不能直接改變store中的狀態</font>。改變store中的狀態的唯一途徑就是顯式地提交(commit) mutation。這樣使得我們可以方便地跟踪每一個狀態的變化，從而讓我們能夠實現一些工具幫助我們更好地了解我們的應用。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>簡單來說:<br>\nVuex 使一個<mark>數據倉庫（狀態管理器）</mark>，用來管理<mark>全域變數</mark></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"Vuex-安裝\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/07/12/vuex#Vuex-安裝\"></a>Vuex 安裝</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>首先 先安裝Vuex</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install vuex --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>在<code>src資料夾</code>底下建立一個<code>vuex資料夾</code>，並且新增檔案 <code>store.js</code></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// store.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> Vue <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'vue'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> Vuex <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'vuex'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">Vue.use(Vuex);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 注意 Vue.Store的 S 一定要大寫</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Vuex.Store({})</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"Component的建立\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/07/12/vuex#Component的建立\"></a>Component的建立</h2>\n<p>在<code>component資料夾</code>底下新增檔案 <code>Count.vue</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"￼2\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/07/12/vuex#￼2\"></a><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// Count.vue</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">template</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">div</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span>{{msg}}<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">div</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">template</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">script</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> store <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">\"@/vuex/store\"</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\"><span class=\"keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"keyword\">default</span> {</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  data() {</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> {</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">      msg: <span class=\"string\">\"hello Vuex\"</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    };</span><br><span class=\"line\">  },</span><br><span class=\"line\">  store</span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">script</span>></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure></h2>\n<h2 id=\"Router的建立\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/07/12/vuex#Router的建立\"></a>Router的建立</h2>\n<p>修改<code>router資料夾</code>底下的<code>index.js</code></p>\n<ol>\n<li>引入 component</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> Count <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'@/components/Count'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>設定路徑</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    path: <span class=\"string\">'/count'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    component: Count</span><br><span class=\"line\">  },</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>把你的router 匯出</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>檔案如下：</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"￼5\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/07/12/vuex#￼5\"></a><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> Vue <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'vue'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> VueRouter <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'vue-router'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 引入自訂的分頁元件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> Home <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'../views/Home.vue'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 引入自訂的 Count component</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> Count <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'@/components/Count'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Vue.use(VueRouter)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> routes = [</span><br><span class=\"line\">  {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    path: <span class=\"string\">'/'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    name: <span class=\"string\">'Home'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    component: Home</span><br><span class=\"line\">  },</span><br><span class=\"line\">  {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    path: <span class=\"string\">'/count'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    component: Count</span><br><span class=\"line\">  },</span><br><span class=\"line\">  {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    path: <span class=\"string\">'/about'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    name: <span class=\"string\">'About'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// route level code-splitting</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// this generates a separate chunk (about.[hash].js) for this route</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// which is lazy-loaded when the route is visited.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    component: <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"params\">()</span> =></span> <span class=\"keyword\">import</span>(<span class=\"comment\">/* webpackChunkName: \"about\" */</span> <span class=\"string\">'../views/About.vue'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">  }</span><br><span class=\"line\">]</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> router = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> VueRouter({</span><br><span class=\"line\">  routes</span><br><span class=\"line\">})</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 匯出router</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"keyword\">default</span> router</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure></h2>\n<h2 id=\"Vuex-模擬流程\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/07/12/vuex#Vuex-模擬流程\"></a>Vuex 模擬流程</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tePvh1U.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"state-狀態\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/07/12/vuex#state-狀態\"></a>state(狀態)</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// store.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> Vue <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'vue'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> Vuex <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'vuex'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">Vue.use(Vuex);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> state = {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    count: <span class=\"number\">10</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Vuex.Store({</span><br><span class=\"line\">    state,</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">})</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"￼7\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/07/12/vuex#￼7\"></a><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// Count.vue</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">template</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">div</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span>{{msg}}<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span>{{count}}<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">div</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">template</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">script</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> store <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">\"@/vuex/store\"</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> { mapState } <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">\"vuex\"</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\"><span class=\"keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"keyword\">default</span> {</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  data() {</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> {</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">      msg: <span class=\"string\">\"hello Vuex\"</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    };</span><br><span class=\"line\">  },</span><br><span class=\"line\">  store</span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">script</span>></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure></h2>\n<h3 id=\"mutation-同步修改狀態\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/07/12/vuex#mutation-同步修改狀態\"></a>mutation(同步修改狀態)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>要修改state一定只能利用 提交mutation的方式</li>\n<li>可以使用<code>$store.commit（）</code> 或是 <code>mapMutation</code>的方式，兩者呈現出來的是一致的</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// sotre.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> Vue <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'vue'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> Vuex <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'vuex'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">Vue.use(Vuex);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> state = {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    count: <span class=\"number\">10</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> mutations = {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    add(state, temp) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        state.count += temp;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    },</span><br><span class=\"line\">    sub(state) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        state.count--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    },</span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Vuex.Store({</span><br><span class=\"line\">    state,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mutations,</span><br><span class=\"line\">})</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"￼9\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/07/12/vuex#￼9\"></a><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// Count.vue</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">template</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">div</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span>{{msg}}<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span>{{count}}<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">// $store.commit（）方式 </span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">button</span> @<span class=\"attr\">click</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"$store.commit('add',10)\"</span>></span>+<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">button</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">button</span> @<span class=\"attr\">click</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"$store.commit('sub')\"</span>></span>-<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">button</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> // 使用mapMutations </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">button</span> @<span class=\"attr\">click</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"sub\"</span>></span>-<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">button</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> //  actions </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">p</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">button</span> @<span class=\"attr\">click</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"addAction\"</span>></span>+<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">button</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">button</span> @<span class=\"attr\">click</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"subAction\"</span>></span>-<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">button</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">p</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">div</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">template</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">script</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> store <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">\"@/vuex/store\"</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> { mapState, mapMutations} <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">\"vuex\"</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\"><span class=\"keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"keyword\">default</span> {</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  data() {</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> {</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">      msg: <span class=\"string\">\"hello Vuex\"</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    };</span><br><span class=\"line\">  },</span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\">  computed: {</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">    ...mapState([<span class=\"string\">\"count\"</span>])</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">  },</span><br><span class=\"line\">  methods: {</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">    ...mapMutations([<span class=\"string\">\"add\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"sub\"</span>]),</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">  },</span><br><span class=\"line\">  store</span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">script</span>></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure></h2>\n<h3 id=\"actions-非同步修改資料\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/07/12/vuex#actions-非同步修改資料\"></a>actions(非同步修改資料)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Action 函數接受一個與<code>store實例</code>具有相同方法和屬性的 <code>context 物件</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>你可以調用 <code>context.commit</code> 提交一個 <code>mutation</code>，</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>或是透過 <code>context.state</code>或<code>context.getters</code> 來取得<code>state</code>和<code>getters</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// store.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> Vue <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'vue'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> Vuex <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'vuex'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">Vue.use(Vuex);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> state = {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    count: <span class=\"number\">10</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> mutations = {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    add(state, temp) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        state.count += temp;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    },</span><br><span class=\"line\">    sub(state) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        state.count--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    },</span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> actions = {</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//     寫法1 context.commit</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    addAction(context) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        context.commit(<span class=\"string\">'add'</span>, <span class=\"number\">10</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 三秒後執行mutations的sub</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        setTimeout(<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"params\">()</span> =></span> { context.commit(<span class=\"string\">'sub'</span>) }, <span class=\"number\">3000</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">'我比sub先執行了'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    },</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//     寫法2 利用解構的方式 處理context.commit</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    subAction({ commit }) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        commit(<span class=\"string\">'sub'</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Vuex.Store({</span><br><span class=\"line\">    state,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mutations,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    actions,</span><br><span class=\"line\">})</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// Count.vue</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">template</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">div</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span>{{msg}}<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span>{{count}}<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">h2</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">// mutations </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">button</span> @<span class=\"attr\">click</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"sub\"</span>></span>-<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">button</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">p</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">// actions</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">button</span> @<span class=\"attr\">click</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"addAction\"</span>></span>+<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">button</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">button</span> @<span class=\"attr\">click</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"subAction\"</span>></span>-<span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">button</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">p</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">div</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">template</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"><<span class=\"name\">script</span>></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> store <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">\"@/vuex/store\"</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> { mapState, mapMutations, mapGetters, mapActions } <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">\"vuex\"</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\"><span class=\"keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"keyword\">default</span> {</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  data() {</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> {</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">      msg: <span class=\"string\">\"hello Vuex\"</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    };</span><br><span class=\"line\">  },</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  computed: {</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">    ...mapState([<span class=\"string\">\"count\"</span>])</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  },</span><br><span class=\"line\">  methods: {</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">    ...mapMutations([<span class=\"string\">\"add\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"sub\"</span>]),</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"actionscript\">    ...mapActions([<span class=\"string\">\"addAction\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"subAction\"</span>])</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  },</span><br><span class=\"line\">  store</span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\"></<span class=\"name\">script</span>></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>資料來源：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://jspang.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">技術胖</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vuex.vuejs.org/zh/guide/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Vue官網</a></li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>","next":{"title":"DesignPattern","link":"2020/06/20/designPattern(class)"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/07/12/vuex/","toc":[{"title":"","id":"Vuex-是什麼？","index":"1"},{"title":"","id":"Vuex-安裝","index":"2"},{"title":"","id":"Component的建立","index":"3"},{"title":"","id":"￼2","index":"4"},{"title":"","id":"Router的建立","index":"5"},{"title":"","id":"￼5","index":"6"},{"title":"","id":"Vuex-模擬流程","index":"7","children":[{"title":"","id":"state-狀態","index":"7.1"}]},{"title":"","id":"￼7","index":"8","children":[{"title":"","id":"mutation-同步修改狀態","index":"8.1"}]},{"title":"","id":"￼9","index":"9","children":[{"title":"","id":"actions-非同步修改資料","index":"9.1"}]}]}